Established in 2006, we build award winning rich media applications, cloud-based business systems, mobile apps and more for the public and private sectors.

For over 13 years, our unrivalled idea base has helped organisations - from start-ups to the established - overachieve their end goals.

To find out what we can do for you, get in touch.

Some of our clients

What we do

Government & Public Sector

We understand how government bodies and local authorities have a requirement to provide value to the communities they serve and how units, departments or even neighbouring boroughs need to share services. Both for public facing and back-office systems, we can streamline existing or help to build new processes.
Corporate & Private Sector

The need to be better than your competitor has never been as important as in the current business climate. Our consultancy services provide development around the key processes that actually matter to your business.


Consultancy and services

Project design & management, UX, Enterprise-class architecture & planning, Service oriented strategies, Change management, Hosted IBM and Microsoft IIS solutions & cloud services, Outsourcing, Systems management
Specialities

Google Android and iPhone app development, Microsoft .net and C# front and back office systems, IBM XWork and Domino, PHP, C & C++, Umbraco CMS, SharePoint and InfoPath forms, Open Architecture, Web Services, XML / XSL and schema design, Advanced web applications (HTML5, compliant CSS3), Mapping and GIS, Legacy database interfacing
